      "details": "\n            \n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row hpt-3 hmr-6\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 mt-2\">\n                    <h2 class=\"jobtitle mb-1 pb-1\">Dreadlocks/Braids/Twist Stylist Boitekong ext1</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h2 class=\"opportunity-company mb-1 pb-1\">Zande Science</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                <div class=\"row verified mb-3 mt-0\">\n                    <div class=\"col\">\n                        <p class=\"verified-text\"><i class=\"icon icon-check2-circle\" style=\"margin-right:2px;\"></i><span>Partner Opportunity</span></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <div class=\"card-detail-meta mt-0\">\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-geo-pin-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Location: </strong>Boitekong, North West</p>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-event-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Date posted:</strong> 05 July 2024</p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-x\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Closing date:</strong> 22 July 2024 </p>\n                            </div>\n                                    <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                        <i class=\"icon icon-cash\"></i>\n                                        <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Salary: </strong>R 9,600.00 per month - Base pay on fixed amount only</p>\n                                    </div>\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-briefcase\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Job type: </strong>Full-time / permanent</p>\n                            </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h6 class=\"opportunity-reference mb-3 mt-3\">Reference number: 1517273</h6>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col text-break\">\n                            <h2>Role description</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p><strong>Join Zibuke Africa's Hair Styling Team!</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Are you a skilled hair stylist passionate about creating stunning dreadlocks, braids, or twists? Look no further! Zibuke Africa, a rising star in the hair industry, seeks talented individuals specializing in these styles.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Quality and Efficiency Matter</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We value stylists who can deliver high-quality and efficient work without compromise. If you're fast, skilled, and focused on dreadlocks, braids, or twists (one or all three!), we want you on our team!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Your Duties</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>- Visit clients at home (we'll handle transportation)</p>\n<p>- Apply our hair rescue lotion to promote hair growth.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>- Create gorgeous braids, dreadlocks, or twists</p>\n<p>- Recommend suitable hair pieces for each client.</p><p></p>\n                            <h2>Role requirement</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p><strong>Assessment and Growth</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Complete a minimum of 15 styles on different clients during assessment. Achieve a rating score of 5.5 or higher to join our team as a full-time stylist.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Join our team</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If you're a skilled, efficient stylist passionate about creating flawless dreadlocks, braids, or twists, apply now and start your journey with Zibuke Africa!</p><p></p>\n                            <h2>Benefits</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p><strong>Competitive Compensation</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>- Basic salary: R3800 - R9600 per month (based customers ratings)</p>\n<p>- Commission: R50 per customer during assessment</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Potential for higher earnings with excellent customer satisfaction</li>\n</ul><p></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n\n                                <hr>\n                                \n        </div>\n    ",
